1oJC4mUIKcExmWHoAw">Mộ - 暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/Nhi%E1%BB%87t-H%E1%BA%A3i-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BB%91ng-Th%C3%B4i-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-ho%C3%A0n-kinh/poem-7PKSPJiR7OpVcwgxW92kiA">Nhiệt Hải hành tống Thôi thị ngự hoàn kinh - 熱海行送崔侍御還京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-C%E1%BB%95-s%C6%A1n-n%E1%BA%A1p-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-VBJQQhCvsc8xNqzBiH_gGw">Thạch Cổ sơn nạp lương - 石鼓山納涼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/T%E1%BB%A9-th%C3%AC-%C4%91i%E1%BB%81n-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BA%A1p-h%E1%BB%A9ng-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-10/poem-YJmZIed96T5P8iGU4bWO_g">Tứ thì điền viên tạp hứng - Đông nhật kỳ 10 - 四時田園雜興－冬日其十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/author-ppK7YKfOyDZw9vIHLHbJVA">Phạm Thành Đại</a>)<br></div>	</div>
